A '''Sage Master''' was a variation of [[Jedi Master]] or [[Jedi sage]] that was established by the [[Jedi Order]]. These Jedi were some of the most powerful Force users the Jedi Order had ever seen, and elitists among other Sages. There have only been two known Sage Masters&mdash;statues of whom were placed upon the [[Processional Way]]'s ceremonial staircase that led to the [[Imperial Palace|Jedi Temple]], alongside two [[Jedi Guardian|Warrior Master]] statues&mdash;but the rank within the Order had been retired until [[19 BBY]] when the Order was destroyed.<ref name="CL" />

